    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>This add-on for <a href=\"https://ithemes.com/exchange/\" title=\"iThemes Exchange\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">iThemes Exchange</a> creates a &#8220;Google Image Search (GIS)&#8221; like layout for products on the store page. This layout will work best for pages with products that have featured images of the same size.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the folder &#8216;exchange-addon-gis-layout&#8217; to the &#8216;/wp-content/plugins/&#8217; directory</li>\n<li>Activate &#8216;iThemes Exchange &#8211; GIS Layout&#8217; through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n<li>Open the &#8216;Addons&#8217; screen through the &#8216;Exchange&#8217; menu in your WordPress dashboard</li>\n<li>If GIS Layout Loop is not enabled, click Enable beside the &#8216;GIS Layout&#8217; entry in the Addons listing</li>\n<li>You can find settings for the addon via wp-dashboard &gt; Exchange &gt; Addons</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; 2016/06/27</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
    "short_description": "Inspired by &quot;Google Image Search (GIS)&quot;, this addon, when activated, will create a new layout for products on a store page.",
